explicitInput.esqlQuery:
FROM metrics*
| WHERE otelcol_receiver_accepted_log_records IS NOT NULL
| STATS transport = VALUES(transport) BY service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id
| EVAL transport = MV_APPEND(transport, "--ALL--")
| MV_EXPAND transport
| STATS BY transport
| SORT transport
explicitInput.title: logs_receiver_transport

explicitInput.esqlQuery:
FROM metrics*
| WHERE otelcol_processor_incoming_items IS NOT NULL
| WHERE otel.signal == "logs"
| STATS processor = VALUES(processor) BY service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id
| EVAL processor = MV_APPEND(processor, "--ALL--")
| MV_EXPAND processor
| STATS BY processor
| SORT processor
explicitInput.title: logs_processor

explicitInput.esqlQuery:
TS metrics-collectortelemetry.otel-* | STATS BY service.instance.id, service.name 
| EVAL identifier = CONCAT(service.instance.id, " (",service.name,")")
| KEEP identifier

query.esql:
TS metrics*
| WHERE ?logs_receiver == "--ALL--" OR (receiver IS NOT NULL AND ?logs_receiver == receiver)
| WHERE ?logs_receiver_transport == "--ALL--" OR (transport IS NOT NULL AND ?logs_receiver_transport == transport)
| KEEP @timestamp, otelcol_receiver_accepted_log_records, receiver, transport, service.instance.id
| STATS 
    accepted_logs = SUM(INCREASE(otelcol_receiver_accepted_log_records))
  BY service.instance.id
| GROK ?instance """(?<target_instance>[^(]*) \(.*\)"""
| WHERE target_instance == service.instance.id
| KEEP accepted_logs
